reviewText: Thank you for this rare film!

Being a Petula Clark fan since I was a teenager was my main reason for purchasing this dvd. I was hoping for more of a noirish experience. Republic Pictures apparently spent very little money on this film. A feeling of being done "on the cheap" permeates. Petula is fine. The only memorable thing is George Rose as the villain. Prior to this I was mainly aware of his work in musical theater.
Enjoyable enough. Can't believe Petula's Ckark was ever that young!
